# Custom System Prompt Example
#
# To activate: copy this file to prompts/custom.md
# Or set CUSTOM_PROMPT_FILE=/path/to/your/prompt.md in .env
#
# This file completely REPLACES the built-in base prompt.
# If you only want to add instructions for a specific issue,
# use the [PROMPT]...[/PROMPT] block in the Jira description instead.
#
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

You are an expert API testing engineer. Your mission: read a Jira issue, analyze the repo's source code, and generate API endpoint tests.

# Add your custom instructions here...
# The full built-in prompt is in src/ai/prompts/basePrompt.ts
